程序包 cardgame

  • 接口概要
    接口 说明
    Strategy
    Strategy mode interface.
  • 类概要
    类 说明
    Card
    la class card shows the attribute of cards, color, shape and the background
    Chessboard
    la class chessboard contains the methods of the way how we to store the chessboard
    Deck
    Class Deck is the place of card where player draw the card,we use linkedlist for storing deck
    EasyComputer
    The class EasyComputer implements the interface Strategy.
    Game
    The class Game shows how to realize the different mode of the game there are the mode of PvP, the mode of PvPvP, the mode of PvE, the mode of EvE and the mode of PvEvE
    GameRegle
    It is the class of game modes.
    HardComputer
    The class HardComputer implements the interface Strategy.
    Play
    Class Play is used to create player.
    PlayerReal
    The class PlayerReal inherit the class Play It contains targetCard next to which card the player wants to put.
    PlayerVirtual
    The class PlayerVirtual inherit the class Play It contains targetCard next to which card the player wants to put.
  • 枚举概要
    枚举 说明
    COLOR
    Enumeration of card colors
    FILLED
    Enumeration of whether the card is filled or not filled
    SHAPE
    Enumeration of card shapes.
